            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName><name ref="Albitius">Albitio</name></persName> filio bone
                        memorie <persName><name ref="Petrus">Petri</name></persName> vende a
                                <persName><name ref="Signorectus">Siniorito</name></persName> filio
                        bone memorie <persName><name ref="Otto">Otti</name></persName> tuisque
                        eredibus idest integra mea portione de <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >terra</rs> inter <rs key="#Consortes/shared_possessions">consortes</rs>
                        aliarum partium quam abeo in loco <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Consortes/shared_possessions"
                            ref="#places/292">Perita</placeName> intro <rs key="#Comitatus"
                            >comitatu</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/154">Rosellensi</geogName> sive in
                        aliis locis et vocabulis ibidem pertinentibus, con tutte le sue dipendenze;
                        pro quibus a te pretio recepi argentum solidi viginti. Pena del doppio.
                        Chiede a <persName key="#Writer #Notary #Judge"><name ref="Romanus"
                                >Romano</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notario</rs> et <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> domni
                        imperatoris la stesura della cartula. Actum aput <rs key="#Local_markets"
                            >mercato</rs> de <placeName key="#Local_markets" ref="#places/291"
                            >Iscla</placeName>. Testimoni: <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Hugo da Sillano">Ugoni</name></persName> da <placeName
                            ref="#places/290">Silano</placeName>; <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Albertus">Alberti</name></persName> filio bone memorie
                                <persName><name ref="Firmus">Firmi</name></persName>; <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Rusticus">Rustico</name></persName> filio bone
                        memorie <persName><name ref="Lambertus">Lamberti</name></persName>. Scrive:
                        Romanus notarius et iudex domni imperatoris.</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
